40|$|The <b>pure</b> <b>premium</b> or {{risk premium}} is the premium that would exactly meet the {{expected}} {{cost of the}} risk covered ignoring management expenses, commissions, contingency loading, etc. Claim frequency rate and mean claim size are required for estimation in calculating risk premiums. In this study, we discussed to estimate claim frequency rate and mean claim size with several methods and calculated risk premiums. Data, which supported our study, is provided by insurance company involving with motor vehicle insurance...|$|R
